From Castersrealm.com:<br>
<br>
EQ ALARM SYSTEM<br>
<br>
A new feature is being experimented with on the Test Server.  Currently when you log in to the Test Server you get prompted to set an alarm to go off after a fixed duration.<br>
<br>
The time is intended to be a true 'alarm clock' to remind people they have real life obligations. It will notify you after you have played for a certain amount of time. There are no plans to make the alarm a spawn or buff timer, so you cannot have multiple alarm clocks operating simultaneously.<br>
<br>
The Alarm should go live in tommorrows patch when more information on how it works should become available. <br>
